How could you leave me alone?

17
00:02:43,720 --> 00:02:45,240
Go get some coffee.

18
00:02:45,320 --> 00:02:46,320
Yes, Master.

19
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:47,480
Add some sugar to it.

20
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:49,400
Since when do you take yours with sugar?

21
00:02:49,480 --> 00:02:51,920
It's not for me. It's for Mrs. Lau.

22
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:54,120
Yes, Master.

23
00:02:54,200 --> 00:02:55,440
Don't call me that.

24
00:02:55,960 --> 00:02:57,080
Go on then!

25
00:02:58,560 --> 00:02:59,800
Yes, Master!

26
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:08,520
I'm sorry.

27
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:10,800
I have some questions to ask you.

28
00:03:10,880 --> 00:03:12,440
It'll give us more leads.

29
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:19,600
Do you know if Cindy
had bad blood with anyone?

30
00:03:21,160 --> 00:03:23,400
She didn't have bad blood with anyone.

31
00:03:24,960 --> 00:03:26,840
She was a kind child.

32
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:30,080
She had many good friends.

33
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:34,480
His daughter and Cindy were good friends.

34
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:36,080
He can testify to that.

35
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:39,760
Did Cindy have a boyfriend?

36
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:40,720
She didn't.

37
00:03:42,600 --> 00:03:45,000
She wanted to focus
on completing university.

38
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:48,200
She wouldn't have wasted
her time on a relationship.

39
00:03:51,160 --> 00:03:52,560
We found traces of semen in her body.

40
00:03:56,720 --> 00:03:57,720
Was she raped?

41
00:03:58,320 --> 00:03:59,320
Was she?

42
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:01,480
Don't get worked up, Mrs. Lau.

43
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:03,760
There are no signs
of her having been raped.

44
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:06,040
The coroner has ruled out
this possibility for now.

45
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:15,880
Do you recognize this high heel?

46
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:23,200
Don't wear
such eye-catching heels next time.

47
00:04:24,080 --> 00:04:25,280
These are branded.

48
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:27,960
A pair of these costs more than $1,000.

49
00:04:30,400 --> 00:04:31,520
All right.

50
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:33,880
Thank you for your cooperation, Mrs. Lau.

51
00:04:34,560 --> 00:04:36,160
Go back and get some rest.

52
00:04:36,240 --> 00:04:38,120
We'll contact you again. Take care.

53
00:04:52,840 --> 00:04:53,800
Master.

54
00:04:54,320 --> 00:04:56,320
