Why are you asking me?

61
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:38,880
Am I that capable?

62
00:05:40,600 --> 00:05:43,920
Can a few pieces of art
trigger someone to kill again?

63
00:05:44,760 --> 00:05:46,000
We're talking about murder.

64
00:05:46,080 --> 00:05:47,200
It's someone's life.

65
00:05:48,960 --> 00:05:50,480
He's the Leap Day Killer.

66
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:53,000
He kills someone every time
the 29th of February comes around.

67
00:05:53,520 --> 00:05:55,000
It has nothing to do with my exhibition.

68
00:05:56,080 --> 00:05:58,520
